            <button onclick="triggerAction('feed')" class="bg-violet-600 hover:bg-violet-500 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded border-b-4 border-violet-800 active:border-b-0 active:translate-y-1 transition-all">È§µÈ£üÊï∏Êìö</button>
